# Byte-exact files: test vectors whose SHA-256 digests are embedded in
# specification documents. CRLF conversion on Windows checkouts silently
# changes bytes and invalidates the recorded hashes. Enforce LF end-of-line
# regardless of platform.
#
# Contributors MUST save these files as UTF-8 without BOM. Git does not
# have a built-in BOM-strip attribute; rely on editor defaults and review
# to keep them clean.
static/compliance/source/test-vectors/plan-hash/** text eol=lf
static/test-vectors/** text eol=lf
